@startuml
[*] -> Assigned : manager and staff assigned
Assigned -> ApprovedAndSigned : everything approved, contract signed
:prepare adverts
ApprovedAndSigned -> AdvertsPrepared : adverts prepared
AdvertsPrepared -> AdvertsScheduled : approve and schedule adverts
AdvertsScheduled -> AdvertsRunning : run adverts
AdvertsRunning -> ExtendOrAdjust : extension or adjustment needed
AdvertsRunning -> Completed : all adverts finished
Completed -> FinalStatementPrepared : prepare final statement
FinalStatementPrepared -> PaymentHandling : handle payment
PaymentHandling : wait for correct balance if overpaid
PaymentHandling : mark as paid if full amount paid
PaymentHandling -> Archived : archive campaign, release staff and managers
@enduml
